  "casesReviews": {
    "category": "Treatment Reviews",
    "title": "Reviews from those who\nvisited Blanche Dental Clinic",
    "items": {
      "0": {
        "name": "Kim Ji*",
        "info": "Female, 22 / Cavity Treatment",
        "content": "Diagnosed with 4 cavities elsewhere, but after examination at Blanche, only 2 were treated and 2 observed. Truly conscientious like on YouTube, valuing natural teeth. Will entrust my teeth to Blanche. Thank you Director ♡"
      },
      "1": {
        "name": "Sung Min*",
        "info": "Male, 45 / Implant",
        "content": "Chose here because the head director operates directly. Many hospitals change doctors, which made me anxious. Thank you for treating me carefully without pain. Highly recommend to friends and family."
      },
      "2": {
        "name": "Ji Soo*",
        "info": "Female, 33 / Implant",
        "content": "Born missing a tooth (haha). Found Dr. Kim Tae-Hyung while searching for an implant ♡ (No secret he's handsomer in person). Implant took just 5 minutes! Removed stitches today and it healed nicely. Will bring my mother too! Director is the best, clinic interior is so pretty."
      },
      "3": {
        "name": "Moon Jun*",
        "info": "Female, 27 / Blanche Laminate",
        "content": "Got laminates elsewhere but didn't consider tooth color, so top and bottom colors were too different and looked artificial. Came for a revision. The color came out beautifully, very satisfied."
      },
      "4": {
        "name": "Park Mi*",
        "info": "Female, 30 / Blanche Laminate",
        "content": "Hesitated due to hearing about laminate side effects. Unlike what I saw online, there was almost no tooth reduction and detailed explanations even for a layperson. The whitening nurse was so kind. The director quickly understood what I wanted and went with minimal (no) prep. Thank you!"
      },
      "5": {
        "name": "Park Sun*",
        "info": "Female, 38 / Blanche Laminate",
        "content": "Whitening was always a concern due to frequent coffee drinking. Heard laminates are possible with almost no tooth reduction. It was done meticulously and beautifully without looking artificial."
      },
      "6": {
        "name": "Yoo Seung*",
        "info": "Female, 34 / Blanche Laminate",
        "content": "Always bothered by uneven bottom teeth compared to top :) Writing this review with great satisfaction as they carefully checked color and shape. Confidence boosted (haha). Thank you Blanche!"
      },
      "7": {
        "name": "Han Ye*",
        "info": "Female, 37 / Implant",
        "content": "Came after watching the director's YouTube. Delayed implant out of fear, but he explained in detail and operated painlessly. Only meant to consult but everyone was so kind I got surgery the same day. Relieved I can come without worries now."
      },
      "8": {
        "name": "Lee Hye*",
        "info": "Female, 31 / Cavity Treatment",
        "content": "Came to change old amalgam to tooth color. Found a cavity via X-ray but treated painlessly. Manager, staff, and director were so kind. ♡ Clean and neat tooth color amalgam replacement >_<"
      },
      "9": {
        "name": "Lee Kyung*",
        "info": "Male, 42 / TMJ",
        "content": "Visited because another clinic couldn't fix my jaw bite. Think it'll improve with regular care. Will sleep comfortably thanks to you. Thank you~ ♡ Fighting!!"
      },
      "10": {
        "name": "Seo Chae*",
        "info": "Female, 35 / Full Arch",
        "content": "First visit today. Great facilities and trendy interior made me happy immediately. Kind hygienist, director, and manager made treatment pleasant. Thank you for the detailed X-ray and checkups. Receptionists were helpful too. May Blanche prosper~ Fighting~"
      }
    },
    "altText": "Patient Treatment Review Image",
